---
Source:
  - Title: The Big Red Book
    Translator: Coleman Barks
    ISBN: 987-0-06-190583-4
Page: 343
By: Rumi
Title: In Love That Long
---
I am here, this moment, inside the beauty,
the gift that God has given, our love.

This gold and circular sign
means we are free of any duty.

Out of eternity I turn my face to you,
and into eternity. We have been in love that long.
